@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ssadzh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (tmp - wp.cos(wp.cos(v2 + 0.70)))
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.abs((v0 + 0.77 / v2 + 0.62)))
    v1 = v2
    v0 = 0.80
    v1 = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v1 + 0.81)) - wp.abs((v1 + 0.07 / v0 + 0.14)))
    v0 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
